      <strong><h4>How Is The Infrastructure Of Gbu ?</h4></strong> <br>
      <p class="fadeuponsc card-text text-justify"> best thing about this college is its infrastructure. You will like the campus. Classrooms and labs are fully air-conditioned. Hostel facility is mandatory for every student, and a single room is allotted to every student. They are maintained well. There are grounds and courts for every sport.
      </p>
